Combine Broccoflower(R), cranberries, onion and half of the almonds in serving dish. Pour dressing over salad; toss to coat. Season with pepper and sprinkle with remaining almonds. Refrigerate until ready to serve. Creamy Dressing: Combine 1/2 cup mayonnaise, 2 Tbsp rice vinegar and 1 Tbsp sugar in a small bowl.